import React from "react"; import { convertColors } from "./../../utils"; import { GnomeCard, Avatar, GnomeInfo, GnomeInfoList } from "./GenderStyled"; const gender = ({to, gnome}) => (

{gnome && gnome.name}

{gnome.professions.length > 0 ? gnome.professions.join(" • ") : "No Profession"}
